  "text": "Here ∞ ± refers to the infinities on the upper/lower sheet. Before we proceed to the genus one case which is the main focus of this paper let us exhibit the construction in the simpler case of genus zero (no gauge symmetry breaking), where we rederive in a very simple way the factorization formulas of Ref. [CITATION_1] .",
